            "title": "Broadcom、Okta和Burlington Stores盤前上漲;StubHub下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a6RCAuwenlClVnuZ1wBDBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEABU081_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國股指期貨週四小幅走低,投資者對中東持續衝突的潛在經濟影響感到擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下是今日<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:盤前交易;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/equities/pre-market?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">盤前交易</a>中美國股市最大的波動股:</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span>Broadcom</span></span></strong> (NASDAQ:AVGO) 股價上漲6.5%,這家人工智能芯片製造商公布的季度業績超出預期,營收和盈利均優於市場預期,並提供了超出預期的當前季度營收指引。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span>Okta</span></span></strong> (NASDAQ:OKTA) 股價上漲1.6%,這家身份管理公司公布的第四季度業績好於預期,佔總營收大部分的訂閱營收增長11%。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span>StubHub</span></span></strong> (NYSE:STUB) 股價暴跌13%,這家二級票務市場公司公布的第四季度營收下降,並由盈轉虧,原因是該公司優先考慮產品開發而非短期增長。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Kroger</strong> (NYSE:KR) 股價下跌0.9%,這家連鎖超市運營商在新任首席執行官領導下,預測年度銷售和利潤溫和,因其正應對不確定的消費環境。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span>Burlington Stores</span></span></strong> (NYSE:BURL) 飆升6.8%,這家折扣零售商公布的第四季度業績超出預期,並發布了強勁的全年展望。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Victoria’s Secret</strong> (NYSE:VSCO) 股價下跌5.9%,儘管這家內衣零售商公布的第四季度業績強於預期,並發布了高於市場預期的指引,但該公司股價在過去一年中已上漲近兩倍。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span>BJs Wholesale Club</span></span></strong> (NYSE:BJ) 股價下跌5%,這家倉儲式會員店運營商公布的第四季度業績未達營收預期,並發布的2026財年指引低於分析師預期。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Ciena</strong> (NYSE:CIEN) 股價下跌3.9%,這家網絡設備製造商公布的2026財年第一季度業績超出華爾街預期,但其全年營收指引遠低於預期。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span>京東</span></span></strong> (NASDAQ:JD) ADR下跌1.5%,這家中國電商公司公布的第四季度盈利未達分析師預期,而營收則基本符合預期。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
