        {
            "title": "油價股票可能進一步下跌的三大原因",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q6h6QwxW6sSH1MqrHXbmsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6U04V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 儘管石油股今年以來強勁上漲,但在過去幾個交易日中已經下跌,<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Bernstein;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Bernstein\">Bernstein</a>分析師表示,推動漲勢的力量同樣可能引發進一步的跌勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Bob Brackett概述了通常導致石油相關股票回落的三個關鍵因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"石油相關股票今年以來上漲有三個原因:對油價的整體貝塔值、板塊輪動以及地緣政治風險溢價,\"<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Brackett;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Brackett\">Brackett</a>寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"石油相關股票同樣會在以下情況下下跌:(1)石油成本過高,導致需求破壞;(2)板塊輪動結束;(3)地緣政治風險溢價下降。\"</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-548e68ff-09ae-3700-acd4-19ec9a71b87a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第一個風險,即需求破壞,目前看來有限。根據Bernstein的說法,油價仍遠低於歷史上引發重大經濟壓力的水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Brackett指出,當能源成本佔全球GDP的約6%時,石油週期往往達到峰值,但\"我們今天遠低於這樣的水平\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"如果石油成本超過5%(我們目前更接近4%),那麼一年後的油價幾乎總是負值(當然石油股票也會跟隨),\"該分析師解釋道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第二個因素是板塊輪動。Bernstein表示,能源股最近的漲勢部分反映了投資者將資金從科技板塊轉移出來。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"對人工智能角色的擔憂促使資金從軟件板塊流向石油板塊,後者感覺不那麼容易受到攻擊,並且在較低油價時有一個合理的進場點,\"Brackett寫道。\"鑑於我們板塊內各股票普遍缺乏上行空間,我們認為輪動逆轉是一個潛在風險。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最後,如果地緣政治緊張局勢緩和,石油股可能會走弱。Bernstein表示,與全球衝突相關的當前風險溢價\"可能持續數週、數月或更長時間\",但持久的解決方案可能會消除該板塊的一個關鍵支撐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-133750784.html",
