        {
            "title": "台鐵「錢磚案」揭地下匯兌黑幕 金管會籲：移工匯款應循三大合法管道",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lWSFJI2u.o9seaW2jZn_vQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/c80f99426fca3b6ee18c841be48b120b\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E9%90%B5-%E9%8C%A2%E7%A3%9A%E6%A1%88-%E6%8F%AD%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E5%8C%AF%E5%85%8C%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%95-%E9%87%91%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83%E7%B1%B2-%E7%A7%BB%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%AF%E6%AC%BE%E6%87%89%E5%BE%AA%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93-125938848.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 21:44:03",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
